text: Ronald Kampamba (born 26 May 1994 in Kitwe, Zambia) simply known as Sate Sate, He is a key player of the Zambian Premier League club Nkana Football Club. ==Career== He began his career with Nkana F.C. in Zambia. He is also a member of the senior Zambia national football team. ==Honours== * Zambian league top score 2 time in season 2012–2013, 2013–2014 * Award of footballer of the year 2014 * Youth player of the year 2013 ==References== Category:Living people Category:People from Kitwe Category:Zambian footballers Category:Zambia international footballers Category:Zambian expatriate footballers Category:Belgian Second Division/Belgian First Division B players Category:Nkana F.C. players Category:Lierse S.K. players Category:Wadi Degla SC players Category:Expatriate footballers in Egypt Category:Expatriate footballers in Belgium Category:2015 Africa Cup of Nations players Category:2015 Africa U-23 Cup of Nations players Category:1994 births Category:Association football forwards
